      <title>根据法庭和解协议，Aetna 将为 LGBTQ 人群提供生育治疗费用</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/aetna-will-cover-fertility-treatments-lgbtq-people-under-court-settlement-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五提交给法院的文件，Aetna 将支付 200 万美元并更新其承保政策，以了结一项诉讼，该诉讼声称该健康保险公司要求 LGBTQ 受益人比异性恋者自掏腰包支付生育治疗费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/aetna-will-cover-fertility-treatments-lgbtq-people-under-court-settlement-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 18:22:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：波音交付延迟导致西南航空飞行员工作时间减少、工资下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/southwest-pilots-face-reduced-hours-pay-due-boeing-delivery-delays-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士表示，西南航空计划减少飞行员的工作时间，实际上是每月支付工资，以应对因波音飞机交付延迟而导致的成本上升和人员过剩问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/southwest-pilots-face-reduced-hours-pay-due-boeing-delivery-delays-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 18:04:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
